# heatmap

### heatmap包

```R
## example("heatmap")
data <- read.csv("Rdata/heatmap.csv",header = T,row.names = 1)
class(data)
## [1] "data.frame"
x <- as.matrix(data) ## 转换为矩阵
heatmap(x)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
heatmap(t(x))
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
heatmap(x,col=c("green","red")) ## col颜色
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
yanse <- colorRampPalette(c("red","black","green"))(nrow(x))
heatmap(x,col=yanse)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
heatmap(x,col=yanse,RowSideColors = yanse)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
heatmap(x,col=yanse,ColSideColors = colorRampPalette(c("red","black","green"))(ncol(x)))
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
heatmap(x,col=yanse,Rowv = NA) ## Rowv，Colv表示行列聚类树图
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
heatmap(x,col=yanse,Rowv = NA,Colv = NA)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```

```

```

### pheatmap包

```
library(pheatmap)
## example("pheatmap")
pheatmap(x)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
annotation_col <- data.frame(CellType=factor(rep(c("N1","T1","N2","T2"),each=5)))
rownames(annotation_col) <- colnames(x)
pheatmap(x,annotation_col = annotation_col)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```
pheatmap(x,annotation_col = annotation_col,display_numbers = T)

### correlation

```
## 样本间相关系数
# 加载pheatmap包
library(pheatmap)  
# 读取表达量矩阵数据，行为基因名，列为样本名
data=read.table("sRNA_TPM_gr_3_credible.txt",header=T,row.names=1,sep="\t")
# 计算样本间相关系数
matrix=cor(data) 
# 将相关系数计算结果输出为txt文件
write.table(matrix,"coefficient_matrix.txt",sep="\t")
# 行和列都不聚类，并且在热图中显示数值
pheatmap(matrix,cluster_rows=F,cluster_cols=F,display_numbers=T) 
```

<img src="http://cdn.liguocheng.top/blog/20200417/tNjLtzzmQP7C.png?imageslim" alt="mark" style="zoom:80%;" />

```
##基因间相关系数

library(pheatmap)  
data=read.table("exp_top30.original.txt",header=T,row.names=1,sep="\t")
data=t(data)  # 对数据做转置；
matrix=cor(data)  
write.table(matrix,"coefficient_matrix.txt",sep="\t") 
#fontsize_number定义了格子中数字的字体大小, number_format 可以控制有效小数的位数
pheatmap(matrix,cluster_rows=F,cluster_cols=F,display_numbers=T,fontsize_number=4,number_format = "%.2f") 
```

<img src="http://cdn.liguocheng.top/blog/20200417/6gKD9SiVPxk5.png?imageslim" alt="mark" style="zoom:80%;" />
